      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Linear elastic titanium alloy (Ti-6Al-4V) with bilinear isotropic hardening for post-yield behavior. Frictional contact (μ=0.2) at screw-rod interface. Required gradation 3: model form justified by literature and sensitivity analysis.",
      "rationale": "Bilinear isotropic hardening parameters sourced from ASTM F136 Ti-6Al-4V coupon data. Sensitivity analysis showed QoI variation < 3% for μ in range 0.15–0.25. Linear elastic UHMWPE vertebral body surrogate consistent with ASTM F1717 fixture specification."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
