      "rationale": "Eleven constructs assembled from production-lot screws and rods, with five tested at Lab A and six at Lab B. Sample size chosen to detect a 10% QoI difference with 80% power at α=0.05 based on prior variability estimates. Lot traceability documented via serialized assembly records."
    },
