      "rationale": "Testing performed exclusively under the ASTM F1717 compression-bending configuration at a single offset distance (50 mm). The COU is limited to this configuration, partially mitigating the gap, but only one test condition was evaluated. This factor falls below the required level and represents a known limitation of the validation dataset."
