      "rationale": "CMM-measured specimen dimensions compared to CAD nominal values; all critical dimensions within ±0.02 mm. Applied displacement rate in FEA (1 mm/min quasi-static) matched test machine crosshead speed. Material property equivalency confirmed via lot-specific MTRs."
